      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m selling my car, and it\u2019s in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s been super dependable for me, runs like a dream, and still looks great parked in the driveway. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a solid, high-quality vehicle without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
