    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and a flawlessly functioning Double-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to address chassis fatigue, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. The suspension retains its signature poise with refreshed bushings and dampers. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including cooling system pressure and compression across all cylinders\u2014remain within factory specifications. This is a purist\u2019s specification, prioritizing visceral performance and structural integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
