    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a wonderful example of a well-maintained driver\u2019s car, offering a perfect blend of luxury and reliability. The exterior paint retains a brilliant gloss, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch, consistent with light, respectful use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is free of rips or stains, showing only gentle softening on the driver's side bolster. All interior electronics, including the navigation system and heated seats, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It features a documented service history with oil changes performed at every 5,000-mile interval. We recently replaced the brake pads and fitted a new set of all-season tires, ensuring the car handles beautifully and stops with confidence. The engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. This is a solid, honest car that has been cared for by a smoke-free owner and is ready for the road.",
      "price": 36500.0,
