    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to own. It\u2019s in great shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable car without the 'brand new' price tag. It runs smoothly, looks sharp, and is totally ready for its next big adventure with you! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
