      "description": "Available now is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing a direct mechanical connection to the M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis dynamics are sharp, benefiting from recent suspension refreshes and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping and light patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals are robust, with a recent valve adjustment and rod bearing service documented. It sits on staggered Style 67 wheels wrapped in high-performance rubber, ready for the apex.",
